<section class="day-section" id="journee">
  <div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto">
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 64px">
      <span class="sec-label">Une journée avec ton compagnon</span>
      <h2>De 8h à minuit — il est <em>là</em></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="day-container reveal">
      <div class="day-timeline">

        <div class="day-item">
          <div class="day-time-col">
            <span class="day-time">08:15</span>
          </div>
          <div class="day-connector-col">
            <div class="day-dot green"></div>
            <div class="day-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="day-content">
            <div class="day-tag avant">☀️ Avant — Préparation</div>
            <h3>Recap de la veille + Agenda du jour</h3>
            <p>Tu ouvres MTC avant TradingView. Hier : +$620, 72% WR, émotion dominante 😎. Aujourd'hui : PMI Zone Euro à 10h00 — ton compagnon te recommande d'éviter EUR/USD entre 09h45 et 10h15.</p>
            <div class="day-pills">
              <span class="day-pill g">Recap hier</span>
              <span class="day-pill g">Objectifs semaine</span>
              <span class="day-pill g">Calendrier éco IA</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="day-item">
          <div class="day-time-col">
            <span class="day-time">09:30</span>
          </div>
          <div class="day-connector-col">
            <div class="day-dot blue"></div>
            <div class="day-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="day-content">
            <div class="day-tag pendant">⚡ Pendant — Session London ouverte</div>
            <h3>Tu trades, il note</h3>
            <p>LONG NQ, breakout confirmé. Tu tapes 3 touches dans MTC — asset, LONG, 😎. Ton compagnon enregistre l'heure, le contexte de marché, ton état. Tout le reste se complète après.</p>
            <div class="day-pills">
              <span class="day-pill b">Trade rapide 3s</span>
              <span class="day-pill b">Live feed</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="day-item">
          <div class="day-time-col">
            <span class="day-time">10:00</span>
          </div>
          <div class="day-connector-col">
            <div class="day-dot blue"></div>
            <div class="day-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="day-content">
            <div class="day-tag pendant">⚡ Pendant — Résultat PMI tombe</div>
            <h3>Analyse en temps réel</h3>
            <p>PMI 52.4 vs 51.5 prévu — surprise haussière. Ton compagnon analyse immédiatement : EUR/USD ▲ BULL, USD ▼ BEAR, NQ neutre. Tu vois l'impact sur tes actifs sans quitter tes graphiques.</p>
            <div class="day-pills">
              <span class="day-pill b">Analyse IA résultats</span>
              <span class="day-pill b">Bull/Bear par actif</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="day-item">
          <div class="day-time-col">
            <span class="day-time">11:42</span>
          </div>
          <div class="day-connector-col">
            <div class="day-dot yel"></div>
            <div class="day-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="day-content">
            <div class="day-tag alerte">⚠️ Pendant — Alerte comportementale</div>
            <h3>Ton compagnon intervient</h3>
            <p>"Tu as atteint 4 trades aujourd'hui. C'était ton objectif max le vendredi — c'est toi qui l'as fixé dimanche dernier." Tu le savais, mais l'adrénaline masquait ça. Lui, il ne l'oublie jamais.</p>
            <div class="day-pills">
              <span class="day-pill y">Alerte objectif</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="day-item">
          <div class="day-time-col">
            <span class="day-time">17:30</span>
          </div>
          <div class="day-connector-col">
            <div class="day-dot purple"></div>
            <div class="day-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="day-content">
            <div class="day-tag apres">🌙 Après — Recap automatique</div>
            <h3>L'email que tu attends</h3>
            <p>Un email t'attend à 17h30 — sans que tu aies rien demandé. P&amp;L du jour, win rate, émotion dominante, une phrase coaching IA personnalisée sur ta session. Tu lis ça avant le dîner. Demain tu seras meilleur.</p>
            <div class="day-pills">
              <span class="day-pill p">Email recap 17h30</span>
              <span class="day-pill p">Phrase coaching IA</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="day-item last">
          <div class="day-time-col">
            <span class="day-time">Dimanche</span>
          </div>
          <div class="day-connector-col">
            <div class="day-dot purple"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="day-content">
            <div class="day-tag apres">🌙 Après — Weekly Debrief</div>
            <h3>Ton bilan de semaine</h3>
            <p>Chaque dimanche soir, ton compagnon génère un rapport complet de ta semaine. Patterns détectés, forces identifiées, 3 objectifs concrets pour la semaine suivante. Tout est prêt quand tu ouvres MTC lundi matin.</p>
            <div class="day-pills">
              <span class="day-pill p">Weekly Debrief IA</span>
              <span class="day-pill p">3 objectifs semaine</span>
              <span class="day-pill p">Score trader /100</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .day-section {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--b);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--b);
    padding: 96px 5%;
  }

  .day-container { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .day-timeline { position: relative; }

  .day-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 40px 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .day-time-col {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding-right: 16px;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .day-time {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--txt3);
    font-weight: 500;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .day-connector-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .day-dot {
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }
  .day-dot.green  { border-color: var(--green);  background: rgba(16,185,129,.15); }
  .day-dot.blue   { border-color: var(--blue);   background: rgba(59,130,246,.15); }
  .day-dot.purple { border-color: #8b5cf6;       background: rgba(139,92,246,.15); }
  .day-dot.yel    { border-color: var(--yel);    background: rgba(245,158,11,.15); }

  .day-line {
    flex: 1;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(var(--b2), var(--b));
    margin: 4px 0;
    min-height: 20px;
  }

  .day-content {
    padding: 0 0 36px 20px;
  }

  .day-item.last .day-content { padding-bottom: 0; }

  .day-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    letter-spacing: .8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .day-tag.avant   { color: var(--green); }
  .day-tag.pendant { color: var(--blue2); }
  .day-tag.apres   { color: #a78bfa; }
  .day-tag.alerte  { color: var(--yel); }

  .day-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--disp);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: -.2px;
  }

  .day-content p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--txt2);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .day-pills {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .day-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    padding: 3px 9px;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }
  .day-pill.g { background: rgba(16,185,129,.08);  color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.15); }
  .day-pill.b { background: rgba(59,130,246,.08);  color: var(--blue2); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.15); }
  .day-pill.p { background: rgba(139,92,246,.08);  color: #a78bfa;      border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,.15); }
  .day-pill.y { background: rgba(245,158,11,.08);  color: var(--yel);   border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.15); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .day-section { padding: 64px 16px; }
    .day-item { grid-template-columns: 56px 32px 1fr; }
    .day-content { padding: 0 0 28px 12px; }
    .day-content h3 { font-size: 15px; }
    .day-content p  { font-size: 13px; }
    .day-container  { padding: 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .day-item { grid-template-columns: 46px 28px 1fr; }
  }
</style>
